      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just hard to feel real when nothing changes. i spend 10 hours a day typing, i eat, i sleep, i wake up and do the same thing. even if i didnt log on tomorrow, or if i just... didnt show up at all, i feel like the world would just keep spinning without a single glitch. like no one would even notice the gap.",
